{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_01","textHome":"当知晓了一切之后，我作为魔法少女的骄傲，@就脆弱地崩溃了……那时，我的内心被@恐怖和绝望充斥。但是现在不一样了。@我为了全新的理念而战斗。我会拯救你的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_18","textHome":"高价的茶具配上红茶和蛋糕。@今天就一起欢迎最棒的终结吧。@对我们来说，毫无痛苦的终结就要开始了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_19","textHome":"神圣的力量，在我的体内流淌……"}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_20","textHome":"为了新的目标……我不会停下脚步……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_21","textHome":"我曾经宣扬的正义太过于渺小。@在我认识到这一点的时候，深深地被震撼了，@但也因此有了现在的我。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_22","textHome":"如果这个世界一定要有恶存在的话，@那可能就是现在的我了。为了把灾祸@转变为幸福，我所做的事情，也可以称之为正义。@是的，我现在就是这么坚信的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_23","textHome":"为了那些仰慕我的人们，我绝不能屈服。@但是，我也一定要冲破围绕在我们魔法少女@周围的真相。因为这就是我重生的意义。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_24","textHome":"又见面了，@你如果没有加入玛吉斯之翼的想法的话，@就不要缠着我了吧？@要是你回心转意了那另当别论。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_25","textHome":"早上开始就要尽心尽力地行动了。@如果有人打算寻找传闻的话，@放松警惕可是会吃苦头的哦？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_26","textHome":"我本不该在学校进行玛吉斯之翼的活动，@但你要是想动手就另当别论了。@你已经做好觉悟了吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_27","textHome":"这之后要去里见那里做蛋糕哦。@我听说那里有用柴火的烤箱。@方便的话你也可以来，还可以听讲座哦？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_03","textHome":"魔女……@为了解放魔法少女必须要拿到悲叹之种……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_28","textHome":"虽然很遗憾，但是正因为是半夜，@所以传闻的警戒必不可少。@虽然你试图钻空子的想法值得表扬，@但遇见了我就只能怪你运气到头了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_29","textHome":"鹿目同学她们不用你来操心。@我会好好告诉她们关于解放的事情的。@她们是值得信赖的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_30","textHome":"请停下你狩猎魔女的行为。@就算魔女化身是解放的证明，@我们依然也是需要悲叹之种的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":300}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_31","textHome":"看来，是想要和我争斗到底了……@要是你看不起我只有一个人的话就放马过来，@我会让你后悔的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_32","textHome":"没想到，会演变成这么大的争端……@明明大家都是为了魔法少女，@真是讽刺……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_33","textHome":"我加入玛吉斯之翼的理由？@没问题，告诉你也行。@只不过，条件是你也要加入我们。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_34","textHome":"我也有一起战斗的同伴。@所以为了她们我也要参与解放……@我不想让她们也和我有同样的经历了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":300}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_35","textHome":"我不知道玛吉斯会引发什么样的奇迹。@但是，那三个人聚集在了一处。@对我们来说，这就是个奇迹。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_36","textHome":"虽然我在神滨找到了喜欢的咖啡馆……@但你要来的话我就不去了。@要是你跟到店里去的话就麻烦了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_37","textHome":"里见那里有好多漂亮的茶具，@在那里煎茶也很有趣。@似乎都是英国的古董品呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_04","textHome":"帮助同志是理所当然的，@只不过一直被叫去帮忙就有些难了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_38","textHome":"这就是年长者的经验吧。@梓很擅长处理人际关系。@所以她成为了玛吉斯三人之间的缓冲物。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_39","textHome":"要作为玛吉斯和黑翼之间的夹层@需要相当的精神力。@那就是对解放的认真程度的表现。@别小看了天音姐妹她们。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_40","textHome":"我有个严肃的问题……@阿莉娜・格雷……成为她作品的模特的话@就暂时不能动了吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_01_41","textHome":"我对自己犯下的沉重罪孽早有自觉！@当自己的正义遭到颠覆时的绝望感！@你能够忍受得了吗！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"tear":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"tear":1}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_42","textHome":"那么，就由我来引领你吧。"}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_43","textHome":"稍微幸福一点了吗？"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_44","textHome":"这就是我展示的道路。"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_45","textHome":"我不会让任何人绝望的。"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_46","textHome":"愿望就是不可侵犯的圣域。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_63","textHome":"我们的希望不容许被夺去。"}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_05","textHome":"那些少女们能接受……这个事实吗……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":300}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_64","textHome":"就让你做个好梦吧。"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_65","textHome":"最终射击・圣夜！"}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_66","textHome":"这是奇迹的礼炮。"}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_02","textHome":"我是巴麻美。@当你辛苦得快要撑不住的时候就呼唤我，@我一定会来拯救你的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_13","textHome":"为了不忘记这个感觉，@就需要一步步地变强才行……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_14","textHome":"就算变强了也没办法安心……@最根本的问题还需要得到解决才行……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_15","textHome":"你还是不知道比较好哦。不该强行打听的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_16","textHome":"在战斗之前最重要的就是平心静气。@现在我需要的是一杯能让我做好觉悟的红茶。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_17","textHome":"最近，我比以前更加珍惜喝红茶的时间了。@像这样能歇一口气的时间，真是无可替代。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]}]},"version":3}